00:00:10.844 --> 00:00:11.595 align:middle
Die!

00:00:11.678 --> 00:00:13.347 align:middle
[HIRO screams]

00:00:13.430 --> 00:00:16.099 align:middle
[ALICIA] How dare you
interrupt my vendetta!

00:00:16.183 --> 00:00:18.268 align:middle
[MIZARISA]
I am Mizarisa the Inquisitor!

00:00:18.352 --> 00:00:21.980 align:middle
You are forbidden from killing
my glorious bed wetter!

00:00:22.064 --> 00:00:24.816 align:middle
[HIRO]
Son of a whore!

00:02:04.291 --> 00:02:07.044 align:middle
[laughing] Fear not, love.

00:02:07.127 --> 00:02:08.921 align:middle
I'm here to protect you.

00:02:09.004 --> 00:02:11.298 align:middle
This... This doesn't make sense.

00:02:11.381 --> 00:02:12.883 align:middle
I'll say it doesn't!

00:02:12.966 --> 00:02:16.261 align:middle
Why's an inquisitor care whether
trash like him lives or dies?

00:02:16.345 --> 00:02:19.306 align:middle
Well, this may be news to you,
but Hiro's been cleared.

00:02:19.389 --> 00:02:20.807 align:middle
City Guard Captain Tesla

00:02:20.891 --> 00:02:23.685 align:middle
ordained the
acquittal personally.

00:02:23.769 --> 00:02:26.772 align:middle
The man holds absolute judicial
authority over the city.

00:02:26.855 --> 00:02:29.983 align:middle
Even the lowliest of peasants
here are answerable to him.

00:02:30.067 --> 00:02:31.693 align:middle
So, in other words...

00:02:31.777 --> 00:02:33.612 align:middle
Harm so much as a
hair on his head,

00:02:33.695 --> 00:02:35.322 align:middle
and you'll find yourself
in direct violation

00:02:35.405 --> 00:02:37.324 align:middle
of an official mandate.

00:02:37.407 --> 00:02:41.286 align:middle
At which point you become mine
to do with as I please!

00:02:42.246 --> 00:02:44.706 align:middle
[HIRO]
Nice! Way to bring it, Mizarisa!

00:02:44.790 --> 00:02:46.959 align:middle
This might just
get her to lay off!

00:02:47.042 --> 00:02:48.293 align:middle
Um. Question.

00:02:48.377 --> 00:02:50.838 align:middle
How'd you even know I was
here in the first place?

00:02:50.921 --> 00:02:53.882 align:middle
Promise not to get upset, but
I've been keeping tabs on you

00:02:53.966 --> 00:02:55.259 align:middle
since you left the dungeon.

00:02:55.342 --> 00:02:57.594 align:middle
I just feel like we should
hang out more, you know?

00:02:57.678 --> 00:03:00.347 align:middle
Wait. You've been tailing
me this entire time?

00:03:00.430 --> 00:03:02.057 align:middle
Kinda surprised I didn't notice.

00:03:02.140 --> 00:03:04.184 align:middle
Let that be a lesson
never to underestimate

00:03:04.268 --> 00:03:06.353 align:middle
an invested inquisitor.

00:03:06.436 --> 00:03:09.857 align:middle
[HIRO] So, like, is she
magical or something?

00:03:09.940 --> 00:03:12.234 align:middle
[REONA] Suggestion:
maybe you should think about

00:03:12.317 --> 00:03:15.028 align:middle
asking her to join your party?

00:03:15.112 --> 00:03:16.905 align:middle
That could work.

00:03:16.989 --> 00:03:19.408 align:middle
[HIRO] True, we sorta
got off on the wrong foot,

00:03:19.491 --> 00:03:22.077 align:middle
but she seems to have my
best interests at heart.

00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:24.288 align:middle
And she's clearly
a good tracker.

00:03:24.371 --> 00:03:27.749 align:middle
Thing is, I have an exceptional
nose. All I had to do

00:03:27.833 --> 00:03:30.169 align:middle
was follow the scent of
your pee pants, and voila!

00:03:30.252 --> 00:03:32.045 align:middle
Wha--? That's not a real skill!

00:03:32.129 --> 00:03:34.923 align:middle
Besides, how strong
could the smell be?

00:03:35.007 --> 00:03:36.466 align:middle
I didn't want to
hurt your feelings,

00:03:36.550 --> 00:03:39.261 align:middle
but yeah,
it's a pretty powerful odor.

00:03:39.344 --> 00:03:41.346 align:middle
Bad enough to make
my eyes water.

00:03:41.430 --> 00:03:43.515 align:middle
You should've said
something earlier!

00:03:43.599 --> 00:03:45.851 align:middle
This is not how I
wanted to find out!

00:03:45.934 --> 00:03:47.978 align:middle
[REONA] This game prides
itself on realism.

00:03:48.061 --> 00:03:51.690 align:middle
Details don't just automatically
reset the way they do in manga.

00:03:51.773 --> 00:03:52.941 align:middle
If you pee yourself here,

00:03:53.025 --> 00:03:55.277 align:middle
you smell like it till
you change clothes.

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:56.528 align:middle
Thanks for the tip.

00:03:56.612 --> 00:03:59.823 align:middle
I'll contact wardrobe as
soon as we're done here.

00:04:03.202 --> 00:04:05.662 align:middle
Damn! So close to his neck!

00:04:05.746 --> 00:04:07.039 align:middle
[HIRO gasping]

00:04:07.122 --> 00:04:10.000 align:middle
Are you crazy? Why'd you
make an attempt on his life?

00:04:10.083 --> 00:04:12.503 align:middle
Did you not hear a
word I just said?

00:04:12.586 --> 00:04:17.090 align:middle
Huh? I didn't hear a thing.
What "mandate?" I'm sorry.

00:04:17.174 --> 00:04:19.885 align:middle
Speak up. I'm rather
preoccupied at the moment

00:04:19.968 --> 00:04:21.845 align:middle
