innocent people?

00:04:34.399 --> 00:04:39.404 align:middle
[laughs] Oh, this might be
my favorite example of nuts.

00:04:39.488 --> 00:04:40.697 align:middle
Have it your way.

00:04:40.781 --> 00:04:43.617 align:middle
