with an inquisitor.

00:04:53.126 --> 00:04:57.214 align:middle
I'm as highly trained
as they, come, girly.

00:04:57.297 --> 00:05:02.010 align:middle
Your brains will be a lovely
addition to the dÃ©cor!

00:05:02.094 --> 00:05:05.639 align:middle
