but this seems like overkill.

00:05:05.722 --> 00:05:07.724 align:middle
[REONA]
Huh?

00:05:07.808 --> 00:05:09.852 align:middle
[HIRO]
Where...?

00:05:09.935 --> 00:05:13.564 align:middle
H-How is that even a thing?
Does she have special powers?

00:05:13.647 --> 00:05:15.691 align:middle
Heads up! She's on the ceiling!

00:05:15.774 --> 00:05:16.817 align:middle
[HIRO gasps]

00:05:18.527 --> 00:05:20.362 align:middle
What kind of childhood
friend is she?

00:05:20.445 --> 00:05:23.198 align:middle
She's like-- She's like
a friggin' ninja!

00:05:23.282 --> 00:05:26.702 align:middle
[laughs] You're both
going to die!

00:05:26.785 --> 00:05:29.788 align:middle
I will slice you open
from skin to pit!

00:05:29.872 --> 00:05:32.207 align:middle
[HIRO gasps]

00:05:33.792 --> 00:05:36.295 align:middle
There! We're okay!

00:05:39.631 --> 00:05:41.675 align:middle
[HIRO]
What? Oh, come on!

00:05:41.758 --> 00:05:43.886 align:middle
Where were you
even keeping those?

00:05:43.969 --> 00:05:46.930 align:middle
[ALICIA cackles]

00:05:47.014 --> 00:05:50.142 align:middle
It appears I neglected to take
your full measure, girl.

00:05:50.225 --> 00:05:52.186 align:middle
It's time for me to get serious.

00:05:52.269 --> 00:05:55.522 align:middle
You're not walking away with
Hiro's blood on your hands.

00:05:55.606 --> 00:05:57.316 align:middle
Liking your style.

00:05:57.399 --> 00:05:59.610 align:middle
[HIRO]
I'm so asking her to join!

00:05:59.693 --> 00:06:03.030 align:middle
Oh, full disclosure: what I
said earlier was a pretext.

00:06:03.113 --> 00:06:05.866 align:middle
My reasons for protectin' him
have very little to do

00:06:05.949 --> 00:06:08.452 align:middle
with the law.
They're quite personal.

00:06:08.535 --> 00:06:11.163 align:middle
What on earth are you
babbling about?

00:06:11.246 --> 00:06:12.539 align:middle
He is exceptional.

00:06:12.623 --> 00:06:15.709 align:middle
When in pain, he shines
like a freshly minted gald.

00:06:15.792 --> 00:06:17.586 align:middle
