following you--

00:06:17.669 --> 00:06:18.795 align:middle
He's my obsession!

00:06:18.879 --> 00:06:20.923 align:middle
I want to torture him
relentlessly!

00:06:21.006 --> 00:06:22.216 align:middle
Push him to the brink.

00:06:22.299 --> 00:06:24.426 align:middle
Sever his limbs!
Squish his eyes!

00:06:24.510 --> 00:06:27.846 align:middle
See him covered in
his own filth! [laughs]

00:06:27.930 --> 00:06:29.515 align:middle
What a spectacle that would be!

00:06:29.598 --> 00:06:32.017 align:middle
My spine tingles
just thinking of it!

00:06:32.100 --> 00:06:34.937 align:middle
Say what?! Why is she
talking like this?

00:06:35.020 --> 00:06:37.105 align:middle
She's just as crazy as Alicia!

00:06:37.189 --> 00:06:38.941 align:middle
Your vengeance
does not outweigh

00:06:39.024 --> 00:06:42.277 align:middle
