compare to a knife!

00:06:58.502 --> 00:06:59.294 align:middle
[MIZARISA grunts]

00:06:59.378 --> 00:07:01.380 align:middle
[ALICIA grunts]

00:07:05.008 --> 00:07:07.719 align:middle
Ha... You freak.
You'll be on my table!

00:07:07.803 --> 00:07:10.681 align:middle
Somehow, I doubt that.
Let me show you a move.

00:07:10.764 --> 00:07:12.891 align:middle
I call it Mincing the Orchard!

00:07:12.975 --> 00:07:14.351 align:middle
[MIZARISA grunts]

00:07:14.434 --> 00:07:15.936 align:middle
[laughs]

00:07:17.563 --> 00:07:19.606 align:middle
[ALICIA yells]

00:07:19.690 --> 00:07:22.234 align:middle
Crap! Not good!
She's on the defensive!

00:07:22.317 --> 00:07:23.402 align:middle
If I didn't know better,

00:07:23.485 --> 00:07:25.362 align:middle
I'd swear she was
aiming for something.

00:07:25.445 --> 00:07:27.990 align:middle
The way a boxer does.
Like a counter move.

00:07:28.073 --> 00:07:29.449 align:middle
[MIZARISA grunts]

00:07:32.786 --> 00:07:34.538 align:middle
