your attacks are simplistic.

00:07:38.083 --> 00:07:41.003 align:middle
It's all in the timing.
I just parry.

00:07:41.086 --> 00:07:42.921 align:middle
[HIRO]
Whoa! Who knew torturer school

00:07:43.005 --> 00:07:45.424 align:middle
