00:07:55.225 --> 00:07:57.060 align:middle
[HIRO]
What? No way!

00:07:57.144 --> 00:07:59.354 align:middle
[MIZARISA laughs]
You're better at this

00:07:59.438 --> 00:08:01.607 align:middle
