peasant girl.

00:08:01.690 --> 00:08:03.609 align:middle
That's a solid
technique you've got,

00:08:03.692 --> 00:08:05.736 align:middle
focusing your attacks
high to open up

00:08:05.819 --> 00:08:08.071 align:middle
