00:08:08.155 --> 00:08:09.990 align:middle
[MIZARISA grunts]

00:08:10.073 --> 00:08:11.366 align:middle
Mizarisa!

00:08:11.450 --> 00:08:16.246 align:middle
[laughs] Don't be upset.
She's just unconscious.

00:08:16.330 --> 00:08:21.126 align:middle
I won't kill her till I'm
done with you. Priorities.

00:08:21.210 --> 00:08:24.713 align:middle
Oh, would you look at that.
There's no one to defend you!

00:08:24.796 --> 00:08:27.090 align:middle
[HIRO gasps]

00:08:27.174 --> 00:08:28.634 align:middle
[HIRO]
Th-This is it.

00:08:28.717 --> 00:08:31.845 align:middle
She's too strong, not to
mention a total freak show.

00:08:31.929 --> 00:08:36.016 align:middle
I'm toast! Death by
a childhood friend!

00:08:36.099 --> 00:08:38.101 align:middle
[KAMUI]
Fighting won't do you any good.

00:08:38.185 --> 00:08:42.314 align:middle
You gotta be clever.
Find another way.

00:08:42.397 --> 00:08:45.609 align:middle
[HIRO] What did he mean?
What can I possibly do?

00:08:45.692 --> 00:08:46.735 align:middle
[HIRO gasps]

00:08:46.818 --> 00:08:50.906 align:middle
Time to die. Time to die.
Time to die!

00:08:50.989 --> 00:08:56.161 align:middle
Run for it! I'll try to distract
her as long as I can!

00:08:56.245 --> 00:08:58.956 align:middle
I sense something otherworldly.

00:08:59.039 --> 00:09:00.457 align:middle
Naughty boy.

00:09:00.541 --> 00:09:03.710 align:middle
You're being safeguarded
by a fairy, aren't you?

00:09:03.794 --> 00:09:04.962 align:middle
[REONA gasps]

00:09:05.045 --> 00:09:07.714 align:middle
[ALICIA laughs]
I do hope she wasn't intending

00:09:07.798 --> 00:09:09.883 align:middle
