00:09:09.967 --> 00:09:12.636 align:middle
Uh. That is not fair! Hiro!

00:09:12.719 --> 00:09:14.429 align:middle
What are you doing?
Get out of here!

00:09:14.513 --> 00:09:17.766 align:middle
