00:09:21.144 --> 00:09:25.399 align:middle
[ALICIA laughs]

00:09:25.482 --> 00:09:27.651 align:middle
[KAMUI] If you were in her
shoes, what's something

00:09:27.734 --> 00:09:30.863 align:middle
an old friend might do
that would throw you off?

00:09:30.946 --> 00:09:32.322 align:middle
[HIRO]
I understand.

00:09:32.406 --> 00:09:36.159 align:middle
