00:09:40.747 --> 00:09:42.165 align:middle
Here goes...

00:09:42.249 --> 00:09:45.711 align:middle
[HIRO yells]

00:09:56.305 --> 00:09:58.557 align:middle
[HIRO]
Yeah! Take that!

00:09:58.640 --> 00:10:00.684 align:middle
No!

00:10:00.767 --> 00:10:04.271 align:middle
Yeah. That how you
thought it'd go?

00:10:04.354 --> 00:10:06.857 align:middle
Uh? Wait, I--!

00:10:06.940 --> 00:10:08.692 align:middle
