twice as hard as that.

00:10:29.880 --> 00:10:33.967 align:middle
Hmph. I suppose you'd like this
to be over with. Very well.

00:10:34.051 --> 00:10:36.803 align:middle
Get on your feet and run away!

00:10:36.887 --> 00:10:39.765 align:middle
[HIRO] Why can't I move?
I don't get it?

00:10:39.848 --> 00:10:42.809 align:middle
Was the kick really that strong?

00:10:42.893 --> 00:10:45.646 align:middle
[HIRO grunts]

00:10:45.729 --> 00:10:49.483 align:middle
Hiro. I'm waiting for you
here--on the other side.

00:10:49.566 --> 00:10:52.861 align:middle
Ah! And evidently,
it's Martin Time again!

00:10:52.945 --> 00:10:54.279 align:middle
I feel it! Yes!

00:10:54.363 --> 00:10:56.573 align:middle
My brother's spirit
is here with us!

00:10:56.657 --> 00:10:59.117 align:middle
Martin. I shall
avenge your death!

00:10:59.201 --> 00:11:01.370 align:middle
Your soul will have justice!

00:11:01.453 --> 00:11:05.415 align:middle
Kill him! Make him pay!
Hiro, must die!

00:11:05.499 --> 00:11:06.458 align:middle
That's a checkmate!

00:11:06.542 --> 00:11:09.086 align:middle
I'm a goner!
Nice knowin' everybody!

00:11:09.169 --> 00:11:11.421 align:middle
[REONA]
Don't give up, Hiro!

00:11:11.505 --> 00:11:13.298 align:middle
[HIRO]
"Auberdine Walkthrough" my ass!

00:11:13.382 --> 00:11:17.928 align:middle
You suck, Kamui! Or maybe I just
don't have your galaxy brain.

00:11:18.011 --> 00:11:22.516 align:middle
Wait. Hold up.
What did he actually say?

00:11:22.599 --> 00:11:25.978 align:middle
[KAMUI] Something an old friend
might do to throw you off.

00:11:26.061 --> 00:11:27.563 align:middle
[HIRO]
Grabbing her boobs! Hello!

00:11:27.646 --> 00:11:32.734 align:middle
