Unless, he meant, like...

00:11:32.818 --> 00:11:37.197 align:middle
Say goodbye. Time to die!

00:11:37.281 --> 00:11:39.741 align:middle
I love you!

00:11:45.747 --> 00:11:48.500 align:middle
